{"tid":1925297,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】BBC 整理 WHO 譚德塞為中國護航語錄  網民：「應上國際法庭告他過失殺人」","createTime":"2020-03-14T09:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T08:17:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9648d9e54a7e746e421fd27c718aa3bd376209b9","tid":1925297,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/9074930-3x2-940x627-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F9074930-3x2-940x627-1.jpg&h=216f5249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎全球疫情失控，很大原因是 WHO 世界衛生組織在疫情爆發初期，過度看小武漢肺炎的嚴重性，加上中國政府對疫情消息封鎖，國民抗疫意識薄弱，到全球各地旅遊散播病毒。而除中國政府管理層外，需要負上較大責任的應該是 WHO 世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Ghebreyesus），BBC 最近就節錄了他的經典發言內容，細看他在疫情爆發初期，到宣佈武漢肺炎為「全球大流行」所講過的談話。<br />\n<br />\n中國疫情大爆發，在 1 月 23 日湖北省多個城市封城時，公開讚賞中國「中國分享疫情信息非常及時，及時採取相應措施，展現出相當高的透明度。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.01.43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.01.43.png&h=670a27b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而到了中國民眾出外旅遊，於全球各地傳播武漢肺炎的時刻，譚德塞在 1 月 31 日表示「世衛反對任何針對中國的旅遊及貿易限制。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.01.50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.01.50.png&h=fefe3416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到了全球開始出現本土案例之後，譚德塞於 2 月 11 日表示「中國以外的疫情傳播可能『冰山一角』，必須團結對抗病毒，確保疫情不會失控。」其後在 2 月 12 日更指「比起恐怖襲擊，病毒能引發政治經濟文化動盪的威力更大，國際應該更積極對抗疫情，把這項病毒視為頭號公敵。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.01.53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.01.53.png&h=707133f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.02.00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.02.00.png&h=2d8b1758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 2 月 21 日他仍然拒絕把武漢肺炎升級為「全球大流行」，卻對中國疫情表示「中國新增病例持續減少，趨勢令人鼓舞。」再於 2 月 24 日表示「現在使用大流行一詞不符合事實，肯定會引起恐慌。」而到了 3 月 11 日，中國疫情爆發情況稍為放緩，反而在歐洲、美洲等地開始大爆發時，譚德塞終於把武漢肺炎升級到「全球大流行」。"},{"pid":"09d722418ef5443d91161173133d59d6894963ec","tid":1925297,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.02.07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.02.07.png&h=274e1e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.02.21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.02.21.png&h=cfd73f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-14-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.02.27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-14-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.02.27.png&h=09b836c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Facebook 上不少網民參與留言，表示譚德塞作為 WHO 世界衛生組織的總幹事，有失職之嫌，更應被告上國際法庭：「這個人國際法庭應該要用過失殺人罪告他吧」「全球大流行你必須負最大責任。」「最荒謬的是沒有一個國家挑戰他那不公正到極點的言論」「武漢肺話」「他根本就是殺人兇手了，我真心希望大家趕快聯合起來罷免他」「The message is loud &amp; clear: WHO is part of China.（顯而易見，WHO是中國的一部份）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2020-03-14_%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884_34_21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596_2020-03-14_%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884_34_21.png&h=77a291c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2020-03-14_%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884_34_44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596_2020-03-14_%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884_34_44.png&h=4c58e62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2020-03-14_%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884_34_30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596_2020-03-14_%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884_34_30.png&h=ac73851c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=640272586539454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fw